                      We Welcome ALL Ship Observations
                       A word about Ship Observations

      GIVING YOU AN ACCURATE FORECAST TAKES ACCURATE INFORMATION. SHIP
   OBSERVATIONS PLAY A VITAL ROLE IN PRODUCING  THE BEST POSSIBLE WEATHER
   FORECAST.  WE DEPEND ON YOU AS MUCH AS YOU DEPEND ON US.  HELP US HELP
                       YOU BY REPORTING YOUR WEATHER.

